# --- HuggingFace model cache --------------------------------------------
# ESM-2 weights are downloaded automatically on first use. Don't commit
# them — they are large and reproducible.
.cache/
~/.cache/huggingface/

# --- Claude Code session metadata ---------------------------------------
.claude/

# --- Local-only scratch --------------------------------------------------
run.log
test.txt
*.log

# --- Submission work artifacts (regeneratable from REPORT.md → pandoc) ---
# REPORT.pdf is the canonical submission. The markdown source, DOCX
# exports, and figure-stripped variants are kept locally for re-rendering
# but excluded from the GitHub repo.
REPORT.md
REPORT.docx
REPORT_for_gdocs.md
REPORT_for_gdocs.docx
REPORT_figure1.png
CLAUDE_CODE_PROMPTS.md

# --- Data (CSVs, calibrations, FASTA, PDBs, figures) are committed ------
# All data files are non-sensitive (no regulated-agent sequences;
# benign-derived test constructs only) and core to the benchmark's
# reproducibility claim. See REPORT §A.4 for the dual-use review.
